<div class="modal fade" id="locationsHelp" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="locationsHelpLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="locationsHelpLabel">Locations Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Purpose</h6>
                    <p>Locations (bins) represent the smallest addressable storage position in the warehouse.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Index (List)</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Select warehouse, sector, section, and structure to scope locations.</li>
                        <li>Filter by zone to focus on staging/picking/quarantine areas.</li>
                        <li>Filter by code or barcode and control activity status.</li>
                        <li>Sort and paginate results.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Create</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Click <strong>New Location</strong> to create a bin.</li>
                        <li>Required: Structure, Code, Barcode.</li>
                        <li>Optional: assign a zone for operational routing.</li>
                        <li>Set level/row/column for addressing.</li>
                        <li>Define capacity limits (max weight/volume) to prevent incompatible allocations.</li>
                        <li>Choose whether the location accepts lot/expiry tracked products.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Details</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Review the location code, barcode, and coordinates.</li>
                        <li>Confirm capacity limits and tracking compatibility flags.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Edit</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Update code, barcode, or coordinates if needed.</li>
                        <li>Adjust capacity limits or tracking permissions when operational rules change.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Deactivate</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Deactivate locations that are no longer in use.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h6>Common Issues</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li><strong>No structure:</strong> create a structure first.</li>
                        <li><strong>Duplicate code:</strong> location code must be unique per structure.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-light border" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
